{"lemma":"جاهِ","slug":"جاهِ","root":"ج.#.ه","root_slug":"ج-_-ه","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-_-ه","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n4895","n6778"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%87%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4895","headword_ar":"جَاهٌ","root":"jAh","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jwh","text_ar":"جوه"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n6778","headword_ar":"جَاهٌ","root":"jwh","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rank, station,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dignity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA, and JK in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wjh","text_ar":"وجه"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the estimation of, the Sultán;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAhapN","text_ar":"جَاهَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) on the authority of Lh, (TA, as from the K, [but not in my copies,]) or, accord. to Sgh, of Ks.: the former word [probably arabicized from the Persian"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAho","text_ar":"جَاهْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but] said to be formed by transposition from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajohN","text_ar":"وَجْهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; this being first changed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawohN","text_ar":"جَوْهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then, to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawahN","text_ar":"جَوَهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and then, to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAhN","text_ar":"جَاهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, accord. to Lh, it is not from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajohN","text_ar":"وَجْهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhot","text_ar":"جُهْت"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhotu","text_ar":"جُهْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first pers. sing. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAha","text_ar":"جَاهَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]; though he does not explain what is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhot","text_ar":"جُهْت"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN *uw","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ ذُو"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAhK","text_ar":"جَاهٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is possessed of rank, station,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dignity"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lifulaAnK jaAhN fiyhimo","text_ar":"لِفُلَانٍ جَاهٌ فِيهِمْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"To such a one belongs rank, station,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dignity, among them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Aboo-Bekr, TA.) The dim. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAhN","text_ar":"جَاهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAhapN","text_ar":"جَاهَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juwayohapN","text_ar":"جُوَيْهَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAhi","text_ar":"جَاهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", indecl., with kesr for its termination; and, accord. to As, sometimes,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAhK","text_ar":"جَاهٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with tenween; (S;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAhi jaAhi","text_ar":"جَاهِ جَاهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAhK jaAhK","text_ar":"جَاهٍ جَاهٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAho jaAho","text_ar":"جَاهْ جَاهْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lh, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juwh","text_ar":"جُوه"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juwh","text_ar":"جُوه","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawoh jawoh","text_ar":"جَوْه جَوْه"},{"kind":"text","text":", (accord. to different copies of the K, but) indecl., with kesr for the termination, [i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juwhi juwhi","text_ar":"جُوهِ جُوهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawohi jawohi","text_ar":"جَوْهِ جَوْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] mentioned in the M, (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAhi laA jihota","text_ar":"جَاهِ لَا جِهْتَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IDrd, TA, [see 1,]) ejaculations used for chiding a he-camel, not a she-camel: (As, JK, IDrd, S, K:) or one says to a she-camel,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAjK","text_ar":"عَاجٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAhK","text_ar":"جَاهٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A 'Obeyd, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ewj","text_ar":"عوج"},{"kind":"text","text":": [or perhaps there is an omission here: I think it more likely that what A 'Obeyd said was that one says to a she-camel"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAjK","text_ar":"عَاجٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and to a he-camel"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAhK","text_ar":"جَاهٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"}],"source_refs":["K","JK","Lh","TA","As","IDrd","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}